title: Undekhi
overview: Show depicts the two aspects of the society - the power-drunk influential people who think they can get away with anything and the oppressed, subjected to years of torture, who finally decide to bring themselves to justice

tv.episodeTitle: We Have Got Ourselves A Deal
tv.episodeOverview: Rinku gets the better of DSP Ghosh. Shashwat and Alice arrive in Manali and are sucked into the desperate situation immediately. Rinku receives a package and realises that the power is shifting away from him. He makes a cunning move.
